漢姆在扮演德雷柏時是以他父親作為模版，{{r|mad}}{{r|gross20100916}}一位穿著得體的商界有力人物，面對著無法操控的改變，心底裡隱藏著自己的不安和混亂。{{r|gross20100916}}。《廣告狂人》在2007年7月19日首播，有約140萬觀眾收看。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/money/advertising/adtrack/2007-08-05-ad-track-madmen_N.htm|title=AMC uses nostalgia to draw marketers|last=Petrecca|first=Laura|date=August 5, 2007|work=USA Today|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2009-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820084536/http://www.usatoday.com/money/advertising/adtrack/2007-08-05-ad-track-madmen_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>旋即這部佳作吸引了一群忠心的觀眾，劇本和漢姆的演出均嬴得強力的支持和高度的讚賞。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》（USA Today）的影評人大讚漢姆的演出，指出他對唐·德雷柏的揣摩和理解十分出色。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/printedition/life/20070719/d_madmen19.art.htm|title='Mad Men': You'll buy what it's selling|last=Bianco|first=Robert|date=July 19, 2007|work=USA Today|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2009-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820085040/http://www.usatoday.com/printedition/life/20070719/d_madmen19.art.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>而《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》（The Boston Globe）的影評人則直接稱讚漢姆為一位「優秀的主演」。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2007/12/29/surprises_from_cables_far_corners/?page=2|title=Surprises from cable's far corners|last=Gilbert|first=Matthew|date=December 29, 2007|work=The Boston Globe|page=2|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064150/http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2007/12/29/surprises_from_cables_far_corners/?page=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>為著他的出色演出，他嬴取了2007年的[[金球獎|金球獎]]劇情類最佳男主角。<ref name="globes">{{cite web|url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/member/31011|title=HFPA — Awards Search|work=[[Golden_Globe_Awards|Golden Globe]] Official Website|accessdate=February 11, 2009|format=[[World_Wide_Web|Web]]|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130113114422/http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/member/31011|archive-date=2013-01-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>亦分別於同年和翌年提名[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]（Screen Actors Guild Award）劇情類最佳男主角和黃金時段艾美獎劇情類最佳男主角，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.emmys.com/celebrities/jon-hamm |title=Jon Hamm Emmy Nominated |accessdate=2011-12-28 |archive-date=2013-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130903112817/http://www.emmys.com/celebrities/jon-hamm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2008/07/23/earlyshow/leisure/celebspot/main4286748.shtml|title=Jon Hamm Happy To Get "Mad" Again|date=July 23, 2008|work=[[The_Early_Show|The Early Show]]|publisher=[[CBS_News|CBS News]]|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2009-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090821020056/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2008/07/23/earlyshow/leisure/celebspot/main4286748.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過分別落敗於《[[黑道家族|黑道家族]]》（The Sopranos）的[[詹姆斯·甘多菲尼|詹姆斯·甘多菲尼]]（James Gandolfini）和《[[絕命毒師|絕命毒師]]》（Breaking Bad）的[[布萊恩·科蘭斯頓|布萊恩·科蘭斯頓]]（Bryan Cranston）。在2008至2011年，漢姆每年都提名黃金時段[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]（Primetime Emmy Award）劇情類最佳男主角，而美國演員工會獎和金球獎則只有2011年沒有提名。

漢姆演出《廣告狂人》期間亦有繼續出演電影，如《[[地球停轉日|地球停轉日]]》。<ref>{{cite news|first=A.O.|last=Scott|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2008/12/12/movies/12stil.html|title=It's All Over, Earthlings (Don't Flee to New Jersey)|accessdate=January 28, 2011|date=December 12, 2008|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2013-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509093440/http://movies.nytimes.com/2008/12/12/movies/12stil.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>儘管電影的評價未如理想，但票房仍然大賺，全球有近兩億三千萬的票房收益。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-day-the-earth-stood-still|title=Day the Earth Stood Still, The (2008): Reviews|date=December 12, 2008|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103160253/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-day-the-earth-stood-still|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=daytheearthstoodstill08.htm|title=The Day the Earth Stood Still (2008)|date=December 12, 2008|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116032105/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=daytheearthstoodstill08.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>他亦主持了三次的NBC長壽綜藝節目《[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]》（Saturday Night Live），分別一次在2008年及兩次在2010年。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2008/09/don_draper_to_host_snl.html|title=Don Draper to Host 'Saturday Night Live'|last=Brown|first=Lane|date=September 19, 2008|work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2009-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208113730/http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2008/09/don_draper_to_host_snl.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/01/31/saturday-night-live-the-best-skits-featuring-host-jon-hamm/|title="Saturday Night Live": The Best Skits, Featuring Host Jon Hamm|accessdate=November 1, 2010|date=January 31, 2010|work=The Wall Street Journal|archive-date=2011-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110420025603/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/01/31/saturday-night-live-the-best-skits-featuring-host-jon-hamm/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Mawuse|last=Ziegbe|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1651171/20101031/rihanna.jhtml|title=Rihanna, Jon Hamm Helm Halloween 'Saturday Night Live' Episode|accessdate=November 1, 2010|date=October 31, 2010|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|archive-date=2010-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203192346/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1651171/20101031/rihanna.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>首次主持時他扮演了不同角色，其中有兩個小品環節就扮演唐·德雷柏。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2008/10/26/jon-hamm-crashe/|title=Jon Hamm crashes 'SNL'|last=Bruno|first=Mike|date=October 26, 2008|work=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-date=2013-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518091203/http://popwatch.ew.com/2008/10/26/jon-hamm-crashe/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也客串了同台的喜劇《[[娛樂揸Fit人|娛樂揸Fit人]]》（30 Rock）六集，客串為女主演[[天娜·菲|天娜·菲]]（Tina Fey）的角色的戀愛對象和鄰居，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/01/21/tina-fey-and-jo/|title=Tina Fey and Jon Hamm talk about coupling up on '30 Rock'|last=Armstrong|first=Jennifer|date=January 21, 2009|work=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=February 10, 2009|archive-date=2013-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131226004727/http://insidetv.ew.com/2009/01/21/tina-fey-and-jo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>亦因而嬴得兩次[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]喜劇類最佳男客串角色的提名。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.columbiatribune.com/weblogs/cool-dry-place/2009/jul/16/hamm-gets-two-emmy-nods/|title=Hamm gets two Emmy nods|last=Bland|first=Pete|date=July 16, 2009|work=[[Columbia_Daily_Tribune|Columbia Daily Tribune]]|accessdate=July 16, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090720080429/http://www.columbiatribune.com/weblogs/cool-dry-place/2009/jul/16/hamm-gets-two-emmy-nods/|archive-date=2009-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

他在2009年時嬴得一部獨立電影《偷來的人生》的主演，是他首次主演一部電影。<ref>{{cite news|first=Dave|last=McNary|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118014689?refCatId=13|title=IFC pays for 'Stolen' rights|accessdate=February 15, 2010|date=February 3, 2010|work=Variety|archive-date=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107122350/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118014689?refCatId=13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Lindsay|last=Robertson|url=http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2010/02/jon_hamms_first_movie_as_a_lea.html|title=Jon Hamm's First Movie As a Leading Man, ''Stolen'', Is Finally Coming Out|accessdate=February 16, 2010|date=February 16, 2010|work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|archive-date=2010-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100220170841/http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2010/02/jon_hamms_first_movie_as_a_lea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而這部電影迴響不佳，《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》（The Hollywood Reporter）影評人認為角色的發展不足規限了漢姆的發揮。<ref>{{cite news|first=Frank|last=Scheck|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/03/05/us-film-stolen-idUSTRE6240BV20100305|title=Thriller? "Stolen" more like a rip-off|accessdate=March 7, 2010|date=March 4, 2010|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|agency=Reuters|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144621/http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/03/05/us-film-stolen-idUSTRE6240BV20100305|dead-url=yes}}</ref>另外他亦有進行聲音演繹，在動畫《[[史力加萬歲萬萬歲|史力加萬歲萬萬歲]]》（Shrek Forever After）配音扮演一頭[[食人魔|食人魔]]首領。<ref name="brogan" />他在電影《[[城中大盗|城中大盗]]》（The Town）與[[賓·艾佛力|賓·艾佛力]]（Ben Affleck）合作，扮演一位[[联邦调查局|FBI]]探員，是一個與唐·德雷柏完全截然不同的角色，對此他表示自己感到十分高興，因為他表示當初「接到約四十份劇本，全部不是設於六十年代的美國，就是將他定為廣告人」。<ref name="brooks20100909">{{cite news|last=Brooks|first=Xan|title=Mad Men's Jon Hamm is the talk of The Town|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2010/sep/09/jon-hamm-the-town|accessdate=September 14, 2010|work=The Guardian|location=UK|date=September 9, 2010|archive-date=2013-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130128003318/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2010/sep/09/jon-hamm-the-town|dead-url=no}}</ref>這部電影普遍獲得支持，並有近一億四千萬美元全球票房賺獲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-town|title=The Town (2010): Reviews|accessdate=December 16, 2010|date=September 17, 2010|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|archive-date=2012-01-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64uWP4kRW?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-town|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=town10.htm|title=The Town (2010)|accessdate=December 16, 2010|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225122104/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=town10.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>他另一個突破性的角色是在《[[詩吼|詩吼]]》（Howl）出演一位辯護律師。<ref>{{cite news|first=Ruthe|last=Stein|url=http://articles.sfgate.com/2010-09-19/entertainment/24010353_1_don-draper-jon-hamm-mad-men|title=Jon Hamm talks about playing Jake Ehrlich|accessdate=September 27, 2010|date=September 19, 2010|work=San Francisco Chronicle|archive-date=2012-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119090422/http://articles.sfgate.com/2010-09-19/entertainment/24010353_1_don-draper-jon-hamm-mad-men|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2010年12月，他客串了[[FOX|FOX]]的著名動畫《[[辛普森家族|辛普森家族]]》（The Simpsons），扮演一位FBI調查員。<ref>{{cite news|first=Andrea|last=Reiher|url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2010/12/jon-hamm-on-the-simpsons-i-was-considering-not-wearing-pants.html|title=Jon Hamm on 'The Simpsons': 'I was considering not wearing pants'|accessdate=December 13, 2010|date=December 11, 2010|publisher=[[Zap2it|Zap2it]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101215000920/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2010/12/jon-hamm-on-the-simpsons-i-was-considering-not-wearing-pants.html|archive-date=2010-12-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>最近他簽約加入了電影《[[老友有喜|老友有喜]]》（Friends with Kids）的演員組，並在片中擔任監製之一。<ref>{{cite news|first=Kaleem|last=Aftab|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/jon-hamm--its-all-started-to-ad-up-2196314.html|title=Jon Hamm — It's all started to ad up...|accessdate=January 28, 2011|date=January 28, 2011|work=The Independent|location=UK|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924154903/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/jon-hamm--its-all-started-to-ad-up-2196314.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==私人生活==
[[File:Jon_Hamm_(2008).jpg|thumb]]，拍攝於2008年[[第60屆艾美獎|第六十屆黃金時段艾美獎]]頒獎典禮。]]
自1997年起，漢姆便與演員、編劇[[珍妮佛·威斯法特|珍妮佛·威斯法特]]（Jennifer Westfeldt）進入長期戀愛關係，<ref name="guardian">{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2008/apr/27/television|title=The interview: Jon Hamm|last=Illey|first=Chrissy|date=April 27, 2008|work=The Guardian|location=UK|accessdate=January 26, 2009|archive-date=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130614000556/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2008/apr/27/television|dead-url=no}}</ref>共同擁有位處洛杉磯和紐約市[[上西城|上西城]]的住宅。<ref name="guardian"/><ref name="post"/>在一次訪談中，漢姆提到他與威斯法特的感情關係，並說到：「我們或許不會有結婚證書，但過了十年，珍妮佛已經超越了一位普通的女朋友。我們知道我們之間的感情很深。對我來說，人們結婚是因為他們想要孩子，而我也不例外」。<ref>原文如下："We may not have a piece of paper that says we're husband and wife, but after 10 years, Jennifer is more than just a girlfriend. What we have is much deeper and we both know that. To me, people [should] get married when they're ready to have kids, which I'm not ruling out."</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nypost.com/pagesixmag/issues/20080803/Why+Everyones+Mad+About+Jon+Hamm?page=2|title=Why Everyone's Mad About Jon Hamm|last=Adams|first=Patty|date=August 3, 2008|work=New York Post|page=2|accessdate=February 11, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090817113216/http://www.nypost.com/pagesixmag/issues/20080803/Why+Everyones+Mad+About+Jon+Hamm?page=2|archive-date=2009-08-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>漢姆和他的女朋友曾一起出現於服裝公司[[Gap_(服飾)|Gap]]的廣告上。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/13/business/media/13adco.html?fta=y|title=Holiday Campaigns Bring on the Humor to Reassure Consumers|last=Elliott|first=Stuart|date=November 12, 2008|work=The New York Times|accessdate=February 12, 2009|quote=The celebrities in the Gap campaign include Jon Hamm of ''Mad Men'' ... with his girlfriend, the actress Jennifer Westfeldt.|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129033528/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/13/business/media/13adco.html?fta=y|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2009年4月，漢姆與威斯法特一起建立了自己的製作公司，Points West Pictures。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jun/03/news/en-hamm3|title=Jon Hamm's a calm 'Mad Men' guy|last=Rosen|first=Lisa|date=June 3, 2009|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=July 6, 2009|archive-date=2009-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091102202810/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jun/03/news/en-hamm3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2009/04/jon_hamm_and_jennifer_westfeld.html|title=Jon Hamm and Jennifer Westfeldt Fight Censorship|last=Barshad|first=Amos|date=April 27, 2009|work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|accessdate=May 1, 2009|archive-date=2009-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430042023/http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2009/04/jon_hamm_and_jennifer_westfeld.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他們亦熱心支持保護動物，並從加州一間動物收容所收養了一條狗。<ref>{{cite web | title= Mad Men Emmy Nominee Jon Hamm stays true to character, is a real lady's mans | url= http://www.animalfair.com/home/mad-men-emmy-nominee-jon-hamm-stays-true-to-character-is-a-real-ladys-man/ | publisher= [[Animal_Fair|Animal Fair]] | accessdate= September 19, 2011 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110925132052/http://www.animalfair.com/home/mad-men-emmy-nominee-jon-hamm-stays-true-to-character-is-a-real-ladys-man/ | archive-date= 2011-09-25 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>

