e Lynch, and Rico Rodriguez: Our bonus Entertainers of the Year covers|accessdate=December 3, 2010|date=December 2, 2010|work=Entertainment Weekly|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029203050/http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/12/02/jon-hamm-entertainers-of-the-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢姆喜愛打高爾夫球和網球。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-09-26-jon-hamm_N.htm|title=A second round for 'Mad Men' star Jon Hamm|last=Clark|first=Cindy|date=September 26, 2007|work=USA Today|accessdate=February 10, 2009|archive-date=2012-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120626040243/http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-09-26-jon-hamm_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>他亦熱愛冰球和棒球，支持冰球隊伍[[聖路易斯藍調|聖路易斯藍調]]（St. Louis Blues）和棒球隊伍[[聖路易紅雀|聖路易紅雀]]（St. Louis Cardinals）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20291001,00.html|title=Jon Hamm and Jenna Fischer Hit St. Louis for All-Star Game|date=July 13, 2009|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|accessdate=July 14, 2009|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914172032/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20291001,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並客串藍調隊的兩個廣告。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://video.blues.nhl.com/videocenter/console?id=48207&catid=782|title=St. Louis Blues: Jon Hamm TV Spot|accessdate=November 6, 2009|publisher=[[St._Louis_Blues_(ice_hockey)|St. Louis Blues]]|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826010302/http://video.blues.nhl.com/videocenter/console?id=48207&catid=782|dead-url=no}}</ref>

